{"tid":976931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我而家真係好嬲！","createTime":"2019-01-10T18:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T08:53:37.000Z","uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"34a52488e018bc951bdb442b4cd708523e778919","tid":976931,"uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T18:45:51.000Z","msg":"（純發洩）屌你幫你上淘寶買嘢，你話信唔過我，唔俾定錢先都算啦。同你一齊攞貨，親手將件貨俾你，你話下次再俾錢，都算啦。過咗好耐問你攞返錢你竟然可以話冇收過貨，仲問返我係咪未俾你。屌你老味雞乸咁大個鞋盒，size又唔撚啱，我點解會攞撚咗啦？？我反轉自己屋企都冇你件貨呀，你又話揾咗好撚耐都冇。而家好啦，我就無端端冇咗兩舊水，你就拍拍羅友乜事都冇，真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n下次冇俾定錢一撚定唔再幫人買嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我係信你真係冇件貨嘅，不過竟然會搞到咁我真係無話可說。"},{"pid":"8c2903b044cd77284fd67bd7f775583ff93031bb","tid":976931,"uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27e2cfa023d5a8970c9910671d897f79ad5c1ed","tid":976931,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:22:04.000Z","msg":"死傻鳩 做嫁娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ce30c9669815cc51edbad32dfaa739f7f6513a","tid":976931,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"你親手比件貨佢<br />\n<br />\n之後你話信佢冇咗件貨<br />\n黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20dec00d5636ca6daeb24294e9b7d79ef5d91bd","tid":976931,"uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ce30c9669815cc51edbad32dfaa739f7f6513a","tid":976931,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"你親手比件貨佢<br />\n<br />\n之後你話信佢冇咗件貨<br />\n黑人問號<img src=\"